---
title: Basil Pesto Jumbo Salmon Roast Dinner  with Summery Panzanella Salad and Zesty Orzo
description: Gather around and get into a summer state of mind! This basil pesto salmon dinner is full of bright and fresh flavours. Zippy lemony orzo with corn and tomatoes is served alongside panzanella salad to make this meal an absolute showstopper.
